<html>
<head>
  <meta charset='utf-8'>
  <title>Thank You!</title>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Thanks <%= name %></h1>
  <p>Thanks for coming to our conference.  We couldn't have done it without you!</p>

  <p>
    Political activism is at the heart of any democracy and your voice needs to be heard.
    Please consider reaching out to your following representatives: (Note: if you do not see a list of legislators, it is because you did not supply a zipcode when you signed in.)
  </p>

  <table>
  <tr><th>Name</th><th>Twitter ID</th><th>Phone</th><<th>Website</th></tr>
    <% legislators.each do |legislator| %>
      <tr>
        <td><%= "#{legislator.firstname} #{legislator.lastname}" %></td>
        <td><%= "#{legislator.twitter_id}" %></td>
        <td><%= "#{legislator.phone}" %></td>
        <td><%= "#{legislator.website}" %></td>
      </tr>
    <% end %>
  </table>

  <p>If you would like to subscribe to mobile alerts about important congressional news, please reply back to this email.</p>
</body>
</html>